snippet.title: Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban | PS2 | 2004 | Video Game Trailer | HQ
snippet.description:
Trailer for the PlayStation 2 version of the Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban video game, based on the book and the 2004 movie of the same name.

Published by EA under the EA Games brand in 2004
Developed by EA UK

Trailer in high quality. Upscaled from the Trailer in original resolution.
